Author: stressedaboutdessert
Text: I heard somewhere that your first thought is what you're conditioned to think and the thoughts that follow are the true reflection of who you are. You felt bad and knew that the first thought was wrong. That's what's important. All the best to you and your friend.

Author: fat_cacao
Text: I'm sorry :(. Try to be kind to yourself. Our ED brains make us think awful shit sometimes. Someone close to me was diagnosed with cancer and lost a bunch of weight from treatment and I legitimately had moments of jealousy. Of a cancer patient. So yeah. You aren't alone <3
